The paper deals with a fundamental algorithm used in many applications related to natural language processing and machine learning, such as speech recognition, information extraction, and string kernels. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the categories of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Sound (cs.SD).
